PrecisAmendments to the TRADE MARKS REGULATIONS guaranteeing all Canadians a means for depositing documents with the Trade-marks Office, facilitating and improving the filing of trade-marks documents across Canada by establishing a method to determine a specific delivery date, and providing the Registrar with flexibility to designate establishments for the delivery of correspondence.
